name: DBSync
tagline: A Linux commandline utility for pushing database changes with codebase changes

[![build status](http://betahoster.com:773/jarrrk/DBSync/badges/master/build.svg)](http://gogreen.co.uk:8083/jarrrk/DBSync/commits/master)

### What is DBSync?

DBSync is a Linux commandline utility allowing for easy database changes between application versions.
